PrecisOrder Amending the SCHEDULE TO THE CUSTOMS TARIFF - (FERRO-CHROMIUM AND CERTAIN AUTOMOTIVE GOODS) which extends the Most-Favoured-Nation Tariff to ferro-chromium originating in a country to which the General Tariff applies and withdraws the benefit of the General Preferential Tariff from certain motor vehicles originating in the Republic of Korea.

precis:
Order Amending the SCHEDULE TO THE CUSTOMS TARIFF - (FERRO-CHROMIUM AND
CERTAIN AUTOMOTIVE GOODS) which extends the Most-Favoured-Nation Tariff
to ferro-chromium originating in a country to which the General Tariff
applies and withdraws the benefit of the General Preferential Tariff from
certain motor vehicles originating in the Republic of Korea.
